data.description: Welcome home! Spacious with lots of natural light. This 2 bed, 2 bath home, is ready to go. Walk in and see custom tile entry way. Beautiful wood floors throughout. Tile floors in both baths. Master bedroom w/large walk-in closet and 4pc bath! Kitchen has plenty of prep space, storage and bonus pantry. Separate dining space. Living room has a cozy fireplace, for those chilly winter evenings. Enjoy the covered patio, w/extra storage room. Rare, detached 1 car garage and 1 reserved parking space. Cherry Creek Schools! All information deemed reliable. However, buyer should verify all information.
